<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pick-axe" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pick-axe,</orth> an axe not with an edge, but with a sharp point: <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.102" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.389" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 389</bibl> (<emph>these poor --s,</emph> i. e. my hands).
